channel.title: Rune-Kingdom [Duel Arena, Different God Wars, 100% Barrows + More]
channel.description:
[center][size=14pt]Rune-Kingdom [Official Release][/size][/center]
Hello, well I haven't been up to coding servers anymore so I decided to release mine to the public to work on. Now the name may seem like it's used alot but someone stole the name from me so this is considered the 'Official Release'. Please leave positive comments and NO flame. :)
[b]Features:[/b]
[*] Good Economy (Have to work for majority of items) [*] Updated PK System With Better Formulas [*] Real GodSword Stances (Walking, Running, Attacking, Specials) [*] Some Customs Go Into Correct Slot Stats Added [*] Full Skilling For All Players [*] HighScores Compatible [*] Duel Arena Has Been Added [*] Different God Wars (Zamorak, Bandos) [*] A New Boss (Shadow Beast) [*] Working 4-Hit Dragon Claws [*] 100% Barrows With Digging Etc. [*] Pest Control With Different Interfaces For Armor + Stats XP [*] Assault With New Interface [*] Fight Caves Improved A Bit (Not By Much) [*] More Monster Teleports Added (Dragons, New Slayer Tower, Etc.) [*] EXP-Lock Feature Added [*] Working Weapon Stats Interface [*] Working Items On Death Interface [*] All Working Prayers [*] + More (Too Lazy To Type Anymore :P)
